# Documentation Access

## Sources

- Architecture → docs/architecture.md
- Tailwind → docs/tailwind-notes.md
- PR Inventory → pr-inventory.md

---

## Section-Based Loading (CRITICAL)

When context is needed:

1. Identify the exact section required
2. Load ONLY that section
3. Ignore all unrelated content

---

## File-Specific Rules

### Architecture

- Use for: system design, data model, search, routing
- Never load full file

### Tailwind Notes

- Use for: styling decisions, class conventions
- Load only relevant rule

### PR Inventory

- Use for: PR analysis, classification, examples
- Never load entire dataset
- Always filter before using

---

## Never Do This

- Do NOT load full documents
- Do NOT summarize entire files
- Do NOT include multiple sections unless strictly necessary

---

## If Unclear

Ask which section or file is needed before loading context.
